ref:_00D7091pB._500Q000N4NYj:ref

Hi Frantz.  I am including my technical team so they can provide more details if needed.

The issue is that the move file counts are smaller than the actionable file counts – in some cases, much smaller.  When this has occurred, there were no apparent errors noted on the job.

Our expectation is that the actionable file and move file have the same file counts – what is expected to move, does move.  If there are any differences, they would be at an acceptable level that is explained with errors noted, such as cannot find the file when it may have been moved between the scan and move job.

Team – is there anything I’m missing or misstating?  Are there some examples that we can send to Frantz that would help clarify the issue?

Thanks everyone!

Lisa Williams
Principal, COO Business Controls
